023/09/armored-core-patch-1.02-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/armored-core-patch-1.02-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/armored-core-6-fires-of-rubicon"><em>《装甲核心 6：卢比孔河之火》</em></a> <a href="https://www.bandainamcoent.com/news/armored-core-vi-fires-of-rubicon-patch-notes-v-1-02" target="_blank" rel="noopener">补丁 1.02</a>似乎解决了游戏早期可能使三个 Boss 更容易战斗的部分问题。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/guides/gaming-guides/best-rpg-games-2974129">2023 年您可以玩的最佳角色扮演游戏</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/fromsoftware">FromSoftware</a>没有具体说明针对Balteus、Sea Spider和CEL240攻击的调整方向。巴尔特乌斯出现在游戏第一章的结尾，然而， <em><a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/armored-core-6-update-appears-to-make-early-game-easier" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Eurogamer</a></em>指出，这仍然是游戏中最强大的 Boss 之一。</p><p>另一方面，《海蜘蛛》结束了第二章，并在第四章遇到了CEL240。目前尚未确定<em>《装甲核心 6》</em>的这个补丁对这三个敌人有何改变，但希望它能够消除游戏中目前的一些困难。</p><p> 1.02 补丁的其余部分旨在添加“平衡调整，让玩家在组装[装甲核心]时能够在游戏的早期和中期建立更多的多样性，并修复错误”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3490791" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3490791" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3490791" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/armored-core-6-punching-run.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/armored-core-6-punching-run.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/armored-core-6-punching-run-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/armored-core-6-punching-run-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/armored-core-6-punching-run-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/armored-core-6-punching-run-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/armored-core-6-punching-run-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" 