;. “We were trying to hark back to sounds we&#39;ve used in the past with a freshness,” Higgenson said while discussing the &#39;Plain White T&#39;s&#39; in a press release.</p><p> He continued: “This one came from a really authentic place of understanding who we are and what we do. I&#39;m more excited than I&#39;ve been in a long time. As musicians, we&#39;re always trying to outdo ourselves or go somewhere we haven&#39;t gone before. Somehow, we figured out how to go to a fresh spot <em>and</em> still sound like Plain White T&#39;s.”</p><p> &#39;Plain White T&#39;s&#39; is set for release on November 17 via Fearless Records. Pre-order the album <a href="https://goodasgoldgroup.us18.list-manage.com/track/click?u=4e19afdafc8aaaac79b7f12ac&amp;id=2381d3e793&amp;e=31843d49fe">here</a> . </p><figure id="attachment_3496166" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3496166" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3496166" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Plain-White-Ts-self-titled-LP-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="Plain White T's self-titled LP artwork. Credit PRESS" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Plain-White-Ts-self-titled-LP-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Plain-White-Ts-self-titled-LP-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Plain-White-Ts-self-titled-LP-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Plain-White-Ts-self-titled-LP-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Plain-White-Ts-self-titled-LP-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Plain-White-Ts-self-titled-LP-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Plain-White-Ts-self-titled-LP-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3496166" class="wp-caption-text"> Plain White T&#39;s self-titled LP artwork. Credit PRESS</figcaption></figure><h3> <strong>Plain White T&#39;s self-titled LP track list is:</strong></h3><p> <strong>1. &#39;Young Tonight&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>2. &#39;Would You Even&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>3. &#39;You Plus Me&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>4. &#39;Fired Up&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>5. &#39;A Little Less Alone&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>6. &#39;LOVE&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>7. &#39;Someone&#39;s Out There Waiting&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>8. &#39;Girl From Pasadena&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>9. &#39;Happy&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>10. &#39;Red Flags&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>11. &#39;Love Keeps Growing&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>12. &#39;Feeling (More Like) Myself&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>13. &#39;Spaghetti Tattoo&#39;</strong></p><p> In 2019, Plain White T&#39;s <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slam-dunk-announce-new-wave-of-acts-for-2019-festival-plain-white-ts-hello-goodboye-2440029">returned to the UK for that year&#39;s Slam Dunk Festival.</a> The dual event, which <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slam-dunk-birmingham-cancelled-due-2019-revamp-fans-arent-happy-2390562">was headlined by All Time Low</a> , took place in May that year at Temple Newsam Estate in Leeds, before heading down south to Hatfield Park.</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/plain-white-ts-hey-there-delilah-tv-show-troye-sivan-tour-slam-dunk-2442999">Speaking exclusively to <em>NME</em> following the announcement</a> , Higgenson said that the band were “excited to bring [their new] songs over to the UK” for the first time, having aimed to perform their 2018 LP &#39;Parallel Universe&#39; across the pond.</p><p> “The album just came out in August and one of our goals was to get back overseas and be able to play some shows,” he said. “So this is like the first time we&#39;ve been able to do that, it&#39;s like, &#39;Alright, we&#39;re getting there, we&#39;re checkin&#39; off our boxes and making our goals happen&#39;. It should be really fun.”</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/plain-white-ts-share-new-track-red-flags-and-announce-new-self-titled-album-3496142">Plain White T&#39;s share new track &#39;Red Flags&#39; and announce new self-titled album</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
